Thai Fresh

name: Madison Public Library - Pinney Branch
directions:
Multiple individual unisex restrooms are located behind the information desk.
Family restrooms with changing table, small toilet, and stool to reach the sink are located near the Children's section.

comment: https://www.oakton.edu/about/title_ix/trans_gender_nonconforming.php The community college is open to the public during operating hours with no id required, but please check website for specific hours and covid/mask requirements. www.oakton.edu

One location: Main brick building, 1st floor, enter door #20 off of Parking Lot D, near Enrollment Center. Turn right past the computer lab and one will be on your left, clearly marked gender neutral.
